commit.message:
sm.6: Fix clock example for copy'n'paste (#14)

Before (note the quotes, man-db 2.12.0):
> (while sleep 1; do date +%T; printf ’\f’; done) | sm -

After:
> (while sleep 1; do date +%T; printf \\f; done) | sm -
